## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in the perspectives presented. Some sources may emphasize certain aspects of colonialism over others, and the historical context can vary significantly between different regions and periods. Additionally, the complexity of colonialism means that its impacts can be interpreted in various ways, depending on the viewpoint of the observer.